Sabrina Lloyd https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sabrina_Lloyd 0 Sabrina Lloyd (born November 20, 1970) is an American film and television actress. She is best known for playing Wade Welles in the science fiction series Sliders and Natalie Hurley in the ABC sitcom Sports Night.
